audience_size_override as "audience_size_override!: Option < i32 >", 
audience_size_override_reason as "audience_size_override_reason!: Option < String >" FROM handle_scorings WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR handle_id = $6::int4) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR status = $8::handle_scoring_status) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR created_at = $10::timestamptz) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR me_json = $12::text) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR tweets_json = $14::text) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR mentions_json = $16::text) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR post_count = $18::int4) AND (NOT $19::boolean OR impression_count = $20::int4) AND (NOT $21::boolean OR ghost_account = $22::boolean) AND (NOT $23::boolean OR inflated_audience = $24::boolean) AND (NOT $25::boolean OR followed = $26::boolean) AND (NOT $27::boolean OR liked = $28::boolean) AND (NOT $29::boolean OR replied = $30::boolean) AND (NOT $31::boolean OR reposted = $32::boolean) AND (NOT $33::boolean OR mentioned = $34::boolean) AND (NOT $35::boolean OR online_engagement_score = $36::engagement_score) AND (NOT $37::boolean OR online_engagement_override = $38::engagement_score) AND (NOT $39::boolean OR online_engagement_override_reason = $40::text) AND (NOT $41::boolean OR offline_engagement_score = $42::engagement_score) AND (NOT $43::boolean OR offline_engagement_description = $44::text) AND (NOT $45::boolean OR poll_id = $46::varchar) AND (NOT $47::boolean OR poll_ends_at = $48::timestamptz) AND (NOT $49::boolean OR poll_votes_updated_at = $50::timestamptz) AND (NOT $51::boolean OR poll_none_votes = $52::int4) AND (NOT $53::boolean OR poll_average_votes = $54::int4) AND (NOT $55::boolean OR poll_high_votes = $56::int4) AND (NOT $57::boolean OR poll_reverse_votes = $58::int4) AND (NOT $59::boolean OR poll_score = $60::poll_score) AND (NOT $61::boolean OR poll_override = $62::poll_score) AND (NOT $63::boolean OR poll_override_reason = $64::varchar) AND (NOT $65::boolean OR operational_status_score = $66::operational_status) AND (NOT $67::boolean OR operational_status_override = $68::operational_status) AND (NOT $69::boolean OR operational_status_override_reason = $70::text) AND (NOT $71::boolean OR referrer_score = $72::boolean) AND (NOT $73::boolean OR referrer_score_override = $74::boolean) AND (NOT $75::boolean OR referrer_score_override_reason = $76::text) $83::boolean OR audience_size = $84::int4) AND (NOT $85::boolean OR audience_size_override = $86::int4) AND (NOT $87::boolean OR audience_size_override_reason = $88::text) ORDER BY
